### Get repositories for a user
GET http://localhost:5000/api/github/repos?owner=torvalds&type=user
Accept: application/json

###

### Get repositories for an organization
GET http://localhost:5000/api/github/repos?owner=dotnet&type=org
Accept: application/json

###

### Get issues for a repository
GET http://localhost:5000/api/github/issues/microsoft/vscode
Accept: application/json

###

### Create an issue (replace owner and repo with a repo you own)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/github/issues
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "owner": "your-username",
  "repo": "your-repo",
  "title": "Test issue from GitHub Cloud Connector",
  "body": "This issue was created via the GitHub Cloud Connector API."
}

###

### Validation error - missing title
POST http://localhost:5000/api/github/issues
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "owner": "your-username",
  "repo": "your-repo",
  "title": ""
}

###

### 404 - non-existent repository
GET http://localhost:5000/api/github/issues/this-owner-does-not-exist-xyz/no-such-repo
Accept: application/json

###

### 400 - missing owner parameter
GET http://localhost:5000/api/github/repos
Accept: application/json

###

### 400 - invalid type parameter
GET http://localhost:5000/api/github/repos?owner=torvalds&type=invalid
Accept: application/json
